  "body": "\r\n***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: User avatar is gone in 1-1 chat (near message bubbles) for a contact who sends me a message. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUser avatar is present in 1-1 chat near message bubbles for a contact who sends me a message. \r\n<img width=\"253\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-05-01 at 19 56 04\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/39483146-249b61fa-4d7a-11e8-8d05-7796ea0ad292.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nUser avatar is gone in 1-1 chat (near message bubbles) for a contact who sends me a message. \r\n<img width=\"390\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-05-01 at 20 01 51\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/39483291-8bf9eb50-4d7a-11e8-897a-3821884ebf7d.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status on two devices and create two accounts (ContacA and ContactB)\r\n- ContactA adds ContactB in contacts\r\n- ContactB sends a message in 1-1 chat to ContactA\r\n- ContactA checks ContactB's avatar next to message bubble he received\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop (360th nightly build)\r\n* Operating System:  Android and iOS\r\n\r\nTF session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8209535/sessions/58/?accessToken=yjxl5z4SbqoxpxGsIOiDaapAexs\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8209535/sessions/58/?accessToken=yjxl5z4SbqoxpxGsIOiDaapAexs\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.16-59-gc145c8a1+ (2486) @58</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
